dc_description_s: This data layer represents assembly districts for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2021.[Census 2010 population collection blocks were used to create Wisconsin Act 43 Assembly and Senate districts and Wisconsin Act 44 Congressional districts in the summer of 2011. The Eastern District Federal Court decision dated April, 11th, 2012 replaced districts 8 and 9 in the City of Milwaukee.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
